# Law of Demeter

Avoid `user.getProfiles().stream().flatMap(p -> p.getRoles()...)` outside `JwtGenerator` / repository layer.

Expose intent helpers (`getRoleNames()`, `isActive()`) when multiple callers need the same traversal.

Repository JPQL/Criteria paths are fine.
